>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 15:09:06 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 17:47:40 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>As album rollouts continue to evolve, fans recently attempted to melt a giant ice block in the middle of Toronto as part of Drake&#39;s &#34;Iceman&#34; announcement. But how did we get here? NBC News&#39; Gadi Schwartz takes a look back at other memorable rollouts, and how they have advanced through the years.</description><expires>2056-04-30T17:46:04.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">now_staytuned_album_rollouts_260430</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/now/video/the-evolution-of-album-rollouts-262471749906</link><media:content url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/now_staytuned_album_rollouts_260430/1/abs/index.m3u8" medium="video"><media:credit></media:credit><media:title>The evolution of album rollouts</media:title><media:player url="https://www.nbcnews.com/now/video/the-evolution-of-album-rollouts-262471749906"></media:player><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_04/now_staytuned_album_rollouts_260430-ytfzxi.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media:description type="plain">As album rollouts continue to evolve, fans recently attempted to melt a giant ice block in the middle of Toronto as part of Drake&#39;s &#34;Iceman&#34; announcement. But how did we get here? NBC News&#39; Gadi Schwartz takes a look back at other memorable rollouts, and how they have advanced through the years.</media:description><media:subTitle type="text/srt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/04/now_staytuned_album_rollouts_260430_1341.srt"></media:subTitle><media:subTitle type="text/vtt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/04/now_staytuned_album_rollouts_260430_1341.vtt"></media:subTitle></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_04/now_staytuned_album_rollouts_260430-ytfzxi.jpg"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 17:42:59 GMT</pubDate><title>The evolution of album rollouts</title><updateDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 17:47:40 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>The Associated Press</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 22:55:32 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>TEL AVIV, Israel — Hezbollah has launched a new weapon against northern Israel in the latest round of fighting: small drones controlled with fiber-optic cables the width of dental floss that avoid electronic detection</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/world/lebanon/hezbollah-adopts-new-weapon-fiber-optic-drones-used-widely-war-ukraine-rcna342990</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/world/lebanon/hezbollah-adopts-new-weapon-fiber-optic-drones-used-widely-war-ukraine-rcna342990</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-04/260430-israel-drone-1529-764719.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1666" width="2500"><media:credit>Efrem Lukatsky</media:credit><media:text type="plain">A wired drone hovering in front of a distant treeline.</media:text><media:description type="plain">A Ukrainian-made fiber-optic drone in the Kyiv region of Ukraine last year. Hezbollah announced it has been using similar drones on Israeli soldiers operating in southern Lebanon or towns on the border.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-04/260430-israel-drone-0a9517.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="2500" width="1667"><media:credit>Zevik Glidai via AP</media:credit><media:text type="plain">A broken drone surrounded by a thick tangle of wires lying on a patch of dry, cracked earth.</media:text><media:description type="plain">A Ukrainian-made fiber-optic drone in the Kyiv region of Ukraine last year. Hezbollah announced it has been using similar drones on Israeli soldiers operating in southern Lebanon or towns on the border.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-04/260430-israel-drone-1529-764719.jpg" height="1666" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 22:55:32 GMT</pubDate><title>Hezbollah adopts a new weapon: Fiber-optic drones, used widely in the war in Ukraine</title><updateDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 22:55:32 GMT</updateDate></item></channel></rss>